General.Name: East 33 Ltd
General.Description: East 33 Limited produces, processes, and supplies rock oysters in Australia. The company operates through three segments: Oyster Farming, Distribution, and Sundry Units segments. It also engages in the growing and wholesaling of live oysters; wholesale and retail distribution of oysters; selling of liquor to retail customers; provision of restaurant services; and online sales of oysters and complimentary products. East 33 Limited was incorporated in 2019 and is based in Tuncurry, Australia.
